parameters:
Yui: "You can't go out from here anymore. If you do, you'll get no
dinner, okay?"

Polka: "The basement storage room... Why am I in a place like this
again..."
Polka: "I understand... Can't be helped, I guess~"

Polka: "Getting back to the subject, the Zaida-G executive Yui-chan
met today, could it possibly be Garves?"
Yui: "Um... Yes, I think he said his name was Garves."

Polka: "The fierce General Garves... If he appeared before Yui-chan,
then it's likely that the monsters of Zaida-G will start to make their
move too."
Polka: "Yui-chan, from now on, it's going to be a tough fight."

Polka: "You'll have to fight opponents far stronger than the regular
soldiers."
Polka: "Just to confirm one more time..."

Polka: "As Pony-Ceres, do you have the courage to continue fighting
against Zaida-G?"
Polka: "If you're scared, it's okay to end it today."

Yui: "What are you saying, Polka? You were the one who forcefully
recruited me, right~"
Yui: "I said no, but you practically forced me, really forced me~"

Yui: "But you know, since I've accepted it, I'm going to see it
through to the end!"

Yui: "Besides, being a heroine of justice! Trying it out, I'm starting
to think it might not be so bad after all!"

Polka: (She must be scared deep down... To not make me sad... What a
kind girl.)

Yui: "Ah, but promise me one thing. You have to endure not leaving the
basement for a little while!"

Yui: "Once the town is peaceful again, I'll take you out so much
you'll get tired of it!"
Polka: "Yes, I understand. Yui-chan... Thank you so much."
Yui: "After we annihilate Zaida-G, you'll have to thank me plenty~!"
Yui: "Right~? Maybe I'll have you treat me to heaps of cake!"
Polka: "You're such a glutton, Yui-chan~! Ufufufufu!"
